Tarot Game in Python

A project to understand Python graphical library Tkinter, also making use of Quantum Random Number Generator (QRNG) for a real
Shuffle in the tarot deck. 

Command line to run: python main.py

Command line to compile in a .exe file: python -m PyInstaller --onefile --noconsole --add-data "images;images" --add-data "Deck.py;." Jogo_Completo.py
